HELP on REOP                            Level %L

  Syntax: /msg %N reop <bot nick>

 Example: /msg %N reop X

   Usage: Reops a service bot on ALL channels it is currently in.
          Note that the user you wish to grant network-wide chanops to
          MUST have the +k usermode set on itself. Ideal for restoring
          ops to a service bot after or during a desynch.
